Budget Tiers explained<\\/h4>\\n
\\nAesthetic differences between tiers are minimal. The difference is in the build quality and materials used.\\n
\\n
\\nBasic Tier:<\\/b> Upgrade your outdoor space without breaking the bank with our Patio & Garden Essentials Renovation tier. This tier offers affordable renovation options that may include simple yet durable materials and professional installation services. We recommend this tier for those with a small yard or budget, but who still want to improve their outdoor living space.\\n\"}

\\n
\\n\\nStandard Tier:<\\/b> Our landscape remodelling level offers a collection of quality materials and services to transform your outdoor space. This level includes resistant materials, as well as professional installation services. We recommend this level for those looking to completely transform their outdoor space with durable and affordable materials.\"}
